{"tid":1237641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"權力過大嘅問題","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:29:05.000Z","uid":115608,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48c852be5c40dfebc792253605f577e6f149329c","tid":1237641,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"由佔中同612大家都睇得出警權過大嘅問題，雖然有監警會，但警察就意見唔接受之餘，態度又照舊。<br />\n<br />\n今次就算係內部調查科查都係冇用，自己人查自己人可以查到啲咩？可以hea你哋就算數。<br />\n<br />\n就算再整多個independent 嘅監察機構出嚟，佢哋冇權嘅話，就同監警會一樣。當個獨立機構係直接under特首(好似ICAC咁)，如果個特首係有心幫班差佬嘅，棧嘥氣。<br />\n<br />\n我諗到嘅就係權力及特權法，但呢個只係唯有就係下次立法會選舉送多啲非建制派嘅人入去先得。"},{"pid":"7b50ef7ca983e1e3a7eb3412403e54253cb5d69e","tid":1237641,"uid":15743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"監警會嘅成員好似係警察<br />\n警察查警察<br />\n你期待會有咩結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dc33dab4957c9df246c817aa195c05d5375e16","tid":1237641,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗<br />\n一定要設立新監警制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1df4e139e0fa3cb9517e0085379742a4cf55342","tid":1237641,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9dc33dab4957c9df246c817aa195c05d5375e16","tid":1237641,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗<br />\n一定要設立新監警制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"冇權嘅話，就只係會係另一個監警會<br />\n<br />\n我係想佢哋有權下互相制衡"},{"pid":"bb996448e8659b5f6ef3a2307269c1eb56ae82ac","tid":1237641,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1df4e139e0fa3cb9517e0085379742a4cf55342","tid":1237641,"uid":1